com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.robot

Class Robot

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.robot.Robot
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BasicSampleBot, BasicSampleBot2, FakeDummyRobot

    public abstract class Robot
extends Object
    An abstract class representing the physical robot. This class is the central hub for most of HAL.

    Creation Date: 2017

    Since:
    0.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Andrew Liang, Level Up, Dylan Zueck, Crow Force, Cole Savage, Level Up
    See Also:
    SubSystem, VisionSubSystem, HALProgram, HALGUI, HALConfig
